<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT11">
<l>vāḻttukavāy kāṇkakaṇ kēṭka cevimakuṭan</l>
<l>tāḻttu vaṇaṅkumiṉkaṇ ṭaṇmalarāṟ cūḻtta</l>
<l>tuḻāymaṉṉu nīṇmuṭiyeṉ ṟollaimāl  taṉṉai</l>
<l>vaḻāvaṇkai kūppi matittu</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let the mouths praise! Let the eyes see! Let the ears hear!</l>
<l>Do bow down lowering the crown [of your heads],</l>
<l>joining unfailingly [your] bounteous hands in reverence</l>
<l>and meditating upon my ancient Māl with a long crown</l>
<l rend="indent">with abundant tulsi wound around with cool flowers.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
